JIRA has a "View Development Tools" permission in permission schemes, which when a user doesn't have that permission means that they don't see the "Source", "Reviews", or "Commits" tabs on issues.

GreenHopper is still displaying commit information in the Issue Detail view for users even if they don't have that permission.

updated to 1.4-rc2 (after DCON-301)

